FBIS4-55171 "dreeu091_p_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-091 Daily Report 11 May 1994 POLAND Dismissal of Markiewicz Deemed Unlawful Dismissal of Markiewicz Deemed Unlawful LD1105121094 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1010 GMT 11 May 94 LD1105121094 Warsaw PAP Polish BFN [Excerpt] Warsaw, 11 May -- Today the Constitutional Tribunal presented an interpretation of one of the regulations in the radio and television broadcasting act, to the effect that President Lech Walesa acted unlawfully when he dismissed Marek Markiewicz from the post of chairman of the National Radio and Television Broadcasting Council in March this year. [passage omitted]
